[[File:Corint_map.jpg|thumb|Lafarn Residential District on a map]]
The '''Lafarn Residential District''' was one of the areas of [[Corint City]], the [[Planet/Legends|planetary]] [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of [[Pirik]]. It was the residential area of the [[City/Legends|city]]. It contained several non-[[Human/Legends|Human]] communities, showcasing the melting pot of Pirik. There were also several [[Restaurant/Legends|restaurants]] and businesses located in the Lafarn area. It was located 14 [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] from [[Uloitir Sea]].<ref name="J10">{{JournalCite|10|Cracken's Rebel Operatives (article)}}</ref>

